snippet.title: MultiVersus - Official Samurai Jack "It is Time" Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Past, present, future, MultiVersus. Gotta get back, back to the past.
Samurai Jack arrives in the MultiVersus timeline at the start of Season 2, July 23.

MultiVersus is a free-to-play platform fighter with an ever-expanding cast of iconic characters and legendary universes, various online modes, in-game events, on-going content-filled seasons, and more.

Check out our updated website: https://go.wbgames.com/MVSWebsite

Questions? Give our FAQ a look see: https://go.wbgames.com/MVSFAQ
